p: Analyzing the emigration results using the ANOVA Kruskallâ€“Wallis test, statistically significant differences were found between the emigration of S. oryzae in the control culture and the emigration in the cultures with the addition of caraway essential oil at all concentrations and time intervals. Statistically significant differences in the emigration of S. oryzae under the influence of different concentrations of caraway oil and L-carvone in each time interval are marked with asterisks in Figure 1 and Figure 2.
